programmes.show_description: Crime drama series. The team investigates a pregnant teenager who refuses to divulge information about the father of the child.
Crime drama series. The SVU has to solve an unthinkable crime whan an entire family is murdered while sleeping.
Drama series about an NYPD unit specialising in sex-related crimes. A congressman asks SVU for help when he is accused of soliciting for underage girls.
NCIS works with the CIA to discover what secrets are being kept by Captain Butler, an elderly former spy with dementia.
When the founder of an AI-infused dating app is murdered, Detectives Shaw and Riley delve into who would want the love-obsessed man dead.
A man in possession of a stolen car explains his unique nickname to deputies. Police go to the same house twice in less than 30 minutes to sort out a messy marital spat.

A daily round-up of showbiz news and gossip from around the world, focusing on celebrities, movies, music and entertainment.
Bury Your Dead: US crime drama series. Tony's undercover mission comes to an end when his car is blown up. Shepard comes face to face with her arch enemy.
Family: The murder of a petty officer leads the agents on a frantic hunt for a missing infant.
Ex-File: The murder of a US Marine at a military base unearths a convoluted love triangle and a possible spy ring.
Powerful American drama series about lawyers and police. The detectives investigate the cause of a wealthy woman's comatose condition.
Vaya Con Dios: Crime drama. The investigation into the death of a man, who was trying to resolve the death of his son in Chile 30 years previously, turns into a murder trial (S10 ep 24).
Endurance: US crime drama. When a disabled boy dies of smoke inhalation during a fire, his parents and a building tenant become suspects.
Swept Away: A cast member in a reality series is killed and the murder is captured on video tape.
Bronx Cheer. The strangled body of a woman is found in the Bronx and the trail of clues leads the detectives to a ruthless drug dealer.
Ego: An investigator with the State Attorney General's Office is found dead in the Manhattan river.
Recoil: Ziva shoots dead a serial killer when an undercover operation reaches a dramatic conclusion.
About Face: Assistant ME Jimmy Palmer finds himself at the centre of a labyrinthine murder investigation when he comes under fire at a crime scene.
Judgement Day Part One: The death of a special agent in LA leads NCIS Director Jenny Shepard on a dangerous sub-rosa mission to finish some classified business.
DNA evidence in a murder case leads Danny and Baez to identical twins with identical alibis. Also, Frank learns Nicky is interviewing for a job at the Justice Coalition.
As Jamie and Eddie's wedding nears, Erin interviews a witness that makes her doubt Eddie's honesty. Danny and Baez unravel the complicated love life of a young man who was murdered.
Crime drama series. Benson helps an exchange student who is traumatised after a cab driver assaulted her.
Crime drama series. The team deals with the feud between a rapper and a competing record artist after the rapper's wife is assaulted at her home.
Crime drama series. Benson investigates a crime of sexual assault from Stone's past. Rollins considers a proposal from Al.
Crime drama series. The murder of a promising new author uncovers secret kept between two reclusive brothers.
Dead Man Walking: Crime series. A nuclear power plant inspector has been poisoned with a lethal dose of radiation and the team races to identify those responsible.
A deputy tries to level with a man who's struggled with addiction for a decade. Security guards at an aquarium warn officers about a man with a gun.

Jessica works on zoo research for her next book when she's drawn into the murder of a worker's fiance who was killed by snake venom.
Identity Crisis: The accidental discovery of a murder victim during a routine training exercise sparks a hunt for a dangerous criminal.
Leap of Faith: A navy SEAL is shot dead while threatening to throw himself from the top of a building. A known Al Qaeda operative emerges as the main suspect.
Chimera: The death of a sailor on board a ship brings the agents into contact with a deadly virus.
Turnstile Justice: Drama series about lawyers and police. After a mother is killed on the subway, the evidence points towards a recently released psychiatric patient .
Dissonance: Jealousy is the suspected motive when a brilliant young violinist is found murdered.
Stand-off: When a suspect is questioned following the murder of a prisoner, the team wonder whether he was acting on orders from the prison authorities.
White Lie: Detectives Briscoe and Green investigate the murder of a couple, with the trail leading to the wife of an army major involved in the war on drugs.
Whiplash: A murder investigation alerts the detectives to a far-reaching fraud involving staged car accidents.
Director Shepard is killed while trying to clean up a secret mission and Gibbs sets out to find those responsible.
Last Man Standing: US crime drama series. The murder of a petty officer uncovers an internal plot to sell highly classified military information.
Agent Afloat: The murder of a navy officer sparks a major security alert on board an aircraft carrier.
Reese and Fusco become caught up in the gang war between Elias and Dominic as it reaches crisis point. Finch and Root follow a clue to Shaw's whereabouts.
Finch and Root race to save The Machine, which has been located by the rival AI, Samaritan.
